---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-5" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 h-full">
    <div class="text-[12px] font-light">
      <p class="leading-snug">
        Hi, I'm Sayeem, a CS student at Toronto Metropolitan University. I'm learning all about building and working on data infrastructure.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-1.5 mb-0.5 text-[12px]">What I've been working with:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[11px] leading-relaxed space-y-0.5">
        <li>Python, SQL, PySpark</li>
        <li>Databricks, GCP & AWS</li>
        <li>Airflow, Power BI, Looker Studio</li>
        <li>Github + Jira too</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-[12px] font-light leading-snug mt-1">
      Off the laptop: soccer, early-morning fishing, strength training, and building things with wood. 
      Music is in anything that moves. Currently reading: The Visible Man by Chuck Klosterman.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>